, regardless of the stellar and AGN feedback strengths. This new\ntool represents a first step toward a more powerful parameter inference,\nmaximizing the scientific return of future HI surveys, and opening a new avenue\nto minimize the loss of complex information due to data compression down to\nsummary statistics.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 6 Oct 2021 18:00:22 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 9 Jun 2022 17:51:53 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 18 Aug 2022 22:20:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-10-12"}
