thon-SciANN codes reproducing the results reported in this\nmanuscript will be made publicly available at\nhttps://github.com/sciann/sciann-applications.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 6 Oct 2021 20:09:09 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-06-22"}
