 results obtained by the hairpin ML bandpass filter\nshow that the circuit performs well in terms of Scattering(S) parameters and\nthe filter size is significantly reduced.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 7 Oct 2021 14:56:41 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-10-11"}
